<span id="freeTextContainer14767263031783582220">I&apos;m glad I finally finished because it was one of those books I kept thinking about when I was in the middle of it and I had trouble getting things done until I knew what would happen. I really enjoyed it, I think it&apos;s hard to write a book with such a complex story line which all ends up coming together neatly in the end. Like some how even the mysticism and twists weren&apos;t over done and felt like they flowed nicely. I think this is one of my favorites now honestly.</span>
  <span id="freeText14767263031783582220" style="display:none">I'm glad I finally finished because it was one of those books I kept thinking about when I was in the middle of it and I had trouble getting things done until I knew what would happen. I really enjoyed it, I think it's hard to write a book with such a complex story line which all ends up coming together neatly in the end. Like some how even the mysticism and twists weren't over done and felt like they flowed nicely. I think this is one of my favorites now honestly.</span>
